## Description {#details}

This class creates clones of input <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> attributes.

It enumerates attributes of input <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a>, creates clone for each attribute, adds cloned attribute to the output <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a>.
